parameters: Memimi: (That lady... her behavior is odd. Could it be...)

Memimi: (Ahhh... she put the cookie in her pocket! It's
shoplifting...!)

Memimi: Excuse me, customer! Um... do you have any items in
your pocket that haven't been paid for yet?

Woman: What?! Are you saying I shoplifted?! You suspect your
customers?!!!?
Memimi: Eeeek, her voice... it's piercing my ears...

Woman: Oh, I see! You're accusing me of being a thief!!
Would you be satisfied if I stripped naked and let you
search me here?!!?

Memimi: Ah... no, that's not necessary... I just meant,
inside your pocket...

Woman: Hah?! You want to grope through a customer's pocket?!
Call the manager!! Manager!!!
Memimi: Oh no, I mean, that's not what I...

Customer: Poor Memimi-chan... got tangled up with a crazy
woman. She's going to keep yelling to blur out the
shoplifting.

Cerburus Octopus: Shut up! I'm trying to focus before a
match... What seems to be the problem, ma'am? I happen to be
the owner of this establishment...
Memimi: (Ah, that's right... he's the manager now!!)
